<sect2 id="index_1intro_sec">
<title>1. Introduction</title>
<sect3 id="index_1intro_pur">
<title>1.1. Purpose</title>
<para>This document describes the software detailed design (SDD) of the application &quot;AXO X1&quot; for the measurement of accelerometer data of company Next Big Thing AG.</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="index_1intro_sco">
<title>1.2. Scope</title>
<para>This document is intended for the people programming and testing the software of the AXO X1.</para>
</sect3>
