<sect2 id="index_1project_env">
<title>2. Project Environment and Tools</title>
<sect3 id="index_1dev_chip">
<title>2.1. Hardware</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>*Microchip** <linebreak/>
AXO X1 hardware uses <ulink url="https://infocenter.nordicsemi.com/pdf/nRF9160_PS_v2.0.pdf">nRF9160 microchip</ulink> from Nordic Semicondutor with integrated LTE modem <linebreak/>
 <bold>Acceleration Sensor</bold> <linebreak/>
Acceleration Sensor used is <ulink url="https://www.analog.com/media/en/technical-documentation/data-sheets/adxl372.pdf">ADXL372</ulink> from Analog Devices</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><bold>Humidity and Temperature Sensor</bold> <linebreak/>
Humidity and Temperature Sensor used is <ulink url="https://sensirion.com/media/documents/643F9C8E/63A5A436/Datasheet_SHTC3.pdf">SHTC3</ulink> from Sensirion Sensor Company</para>
<para><bold>FRAM</bold> <linebreak/>
FRAM (Ferroelectric Random Access Memory) chip used is Fujitsu Semicondutor <ulink url="https://www.mouser.com/datasheet/2/1113/MB85RS4MTY_DS501_00065_0v1_E-2329189.pdf">MB85RS4MTY</ulink> with 512 KByte memory and SPI interface</para>
<para><bold>Boost Converter</bold> <linebreak/>
As boost converter <ulink url="https://www.mouser.com/datasheet/2/760/XC9145-3178685.pdf">XC9145</ulink> step-up DC/DC converter of Torex Semiconductor is used</para>
<para><bold>Schematic</bold> <ulink url="file://./Prometheus_for_AxoTrack_Mk5.4rn.pdf">Prometheus_for_AxoTrack_Mk5.4rn.pdf</ulink></para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="index_1dev_os">
<title>2.2. Operating System</title>
<para>As operating system <ulink url="https://www.zephyrproject.org/">Zephyr RTOS</ulink> is used in AXO X1 project, used version is 3.2.99.</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="index_1dev_toolchain">
<title>2.1. Software development tools</title>
<para>Visual Studio Code is used as development environment. The environment can be seup in a docker container or plain on an Linux Ubuntu 10.04 computer. Environment setup process is explained in detail <ulink url="https://github.com/next-big-thing-ag/prometheus-xl-firmware">AXO GitHub repository main page</ulink> <simplesect kind="note"><para>Setting up the docker container under windows will fail, because link generation is part of the setup process and is designed only for Linus links.</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="index_1dev_test">
<title>2.3. Test Tools</title>
<para>AXO X1 firmware uses the Zephyr test framework <ulink url="https://docs.zephyrproject.org/latest/develop/test/ztest.html">Ztest</ulink>. For code coverage gcc tool <ulink url="https://gcovr.com/en/stable/guide.html">gcov</ulink> is used.</para>
<para><hruler/>
 </para>
</sect3>
